skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Stop doing hours of research to win your fantasy league, our flash briefing aims to give you a daily one-minute update on all things fantasy! 

Using our skill you get: 
- Rankings
- Breaking news
- Weekly waiver wire adds
- Weekly streams
- Start recommendations
- Trade talk
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
